Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: UN Leader Mr Boutros Boutros-Ghali
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yq20z
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 20 Dec 1996
A tribute to Mr Boutros Boutros-Ghali, former leader of the UN General Assembly, whose peacekeeping skills were put to the test during the Rwandan Genocide.